      "rationale": "The bilinear isotropic hardening model was calibrated against published Ti-6Al-4V tensile coupon data. Augmented Lagrange contact with friction coefficient 0.2 was validated against torque-angle data from screw-rod interface experiments. Model form is appropriate for the compression-bending loading regime."
