      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and tangent modulus were taken from certified material test reports for the production Ti-6Al-4V bar stock. Critical geometric dimensions (thread pitch, core diameter, rod diameter) were confirmed by CMM measurement of five production screws. Input uncertainty propagated through a sensitivity analysis."
