      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under a single ASTM F1717 standardized load configuration (compression-bending at 5 mm/min crosshead speed, ambient conditions). No additional load levels or physiological saline conditioning were applied. Achieved level 2 is below the required level 3; this shortfall is acknowledged and accepted given corroborating analytical evidence."
